  "translations": {
    "en": "Then he said: And Abu al-Hasan Ali ibn Malik al-Nahwi recited to me verses by Mahmud al-Warraq: 'O censurer, I did not commit sins out of ignorance, nor were they another's doing, nor mine; nor out of insolence toward God, nor because my ignorance overcame my intellect; but I hold favourable expectation of the forgiveness of the One peerless in gracious deeds and bounty. If my expectation proves true, in His bounty is confirmation for one like me; and if punishment befalls me, it came by way of fairness in judgment and justice.'",
    "ur": "پھر محمود وراق کے اشعار: 'اے ملامت کرنے والے، گناہ جہالت سے نہیں کیے، بلکہ معافی پر حسن ظن سے۔'",
    "tr": "Mahmud el-Verrak'ın şiiri: 'Ey kınayıcı, cehaletle değil, güzel işlerde eşsiz olanın affına güzel zanla yaptım.'",
    "fa": "اشعار محمود ورّاق: 'ای سرزنشگر، از جهل نیاوردم، بلکه به بخشش یکتا حسن ظن دارم.'",
    "id": "Syair Mahmud al-Warraq: 'Wahai pencela, bukan kebodohan, tetapi berbaik sangka pada ampunan Yang tiada bandingan.'",
    "bn": "মাহমুদ আল-ওয়াররাকের কবিতা: 'হে নিন্দুক, অজ্ঞতাবশত নয়, বরং অদ্বিতীয় সত্তার ক্ষমায় সুধারণায়ে।'",
    "es": "Versos de Mahmud al-Warraq: 'No por ignorancia ni insolencia, sino con buena expectativa del perdón de Aquel sin par.'",
    "fr": "Vers de Mahmud al-Warraq : 'Pas par ignorance ni insolence, mais avec bonne attente du pardon de Celui sans égal.'",
    "de": "Verse von Mahmud al-Warraq: 'Nicht aus Unwissenheit, sondern mit guter Erwartung an Vergebung des Einzigartigen.'",
    "ru": "Стихи Махмуда аль-Варрака: 'Не по невежеству, но с благоприятным ожиданием прощения Того, Кто единственен.'",
    "zh": "马哈穆德·瓦拉克的诗：'并非无知，而是怀着对独一无二者宽恕的美好期望。'"
  }
